Onion seeds are the second seeds able to be grown in allotment patches. They give 9.5 experience points for planting, and take 40 minutes to grow into a harvestable crop. When picking from an allotment patch, they give 10.5 experience points for each onion received.

They may be pickpocketed from a Master Farmers with 38 Thieving, or from seed stall with 27 Thieving. There is also a small chance to obtain them when picking onions from an onion field.
